snippet.title: Attack on Hex Island Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist and play the early access demo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2305380/Attack_on_Hex_Island/

Join our Discord. We'd love to hear your feedback!
https://discord.gg/xWxN6CVTbP

Do you love that one card game in final fantasy and enjoy collecting creatures like in Pokémon? Then you will LOVE playing this game! Come play now! :D
